HOW TO CREATE REPOSITORY

go to your profile 
click on repositories
click on new (which is on right side of repositories page)
enter repository name (which is not availavle in your repository section)
scroll down
click on Create Repository button

HOW TO RENAME YOUR REPOSITORY

go to your repository page
click on repository (which you want to rename)
click on setting
enter your change repository name (this is available on the top when you click on setting)
click on rename


HOW TO DELETE REPOSITORY

go in side of your repository 
click on setting 
scroll down at the end
go to Danger Zone -> delete this repository
